2. DESCRIPTION
--------------

FML-Bot is a modular IRC Bot coded in PHP that can perform many helpful
tasks to make everyday irc'ing easier or fun.

ATTENTION: By using this software, you are stating
that you have read and agreed to the terms in docs/LICENSE.

3. INSTALLATION
---------------

See docs/INSTALL for information on how to install FML-Bot

4. GETTING SUPPORT
------------------

Should you need any help with FML-Bot, please drop by
our IRC chatroom:

Host: irc.connecttek.net
Port: 6667 | SSL: 6697
Channel: #fml


5. REPORTING BUGS
-----------------

Should you come across a bug within the original code, please
report it to us by visiting our IRC ChatRoom stated above